		<title>紐元兌美元因紐儲行強硬通膨言論而上漲</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/nzdusd-gains-hawkish-rbnz-inflation-comments</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 01:54:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
